race.comment: SMOOTH PANTHER (1) charged out of the boxes with a fast early split and led throughout to score when a 5.5 lengths winner (19.79) over 352m at this track. Well placed and can measure up. FARMOR ENVY (2) was in the money last time at this track (19.79) in a Grade 3/4, finishing a 1.3 lengths second. Has already won three times from this draw. Looks a key chance on best figures. OUT OF AUSTRIAN (7) was out of the placings last time but shapes well for this on his convincing win a few runs back, getting around this track over 352m in 19.56. Expected to feature on best figures. WHO'S THE MAN (8) is worth consideration.
